It does not do so according to the genera predictable and apprehended (abstract biographical, life and work), but by seeking something similar to the nucleus of ignition of character created.
The trip is exciting and Vincent spares neither fear nor illuminations.
Delicious pleasure, this book is also an invitation moving to readings and reviews.
I leave you here a few snapshots.
